{"tid":144883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西九高鐵站內含戰術支援辦公室及羈留設施","createTime":"2017-03-05T19:42:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-05T19:45:07.000Z","uid":22054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0ed5489526a860db3417a9b56b953d2d7b4db262","tid":144883,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T19:42:34.000Z","msg":"明報獲得兩份高鐵西九龍總站詳細設計文件修訂版本，文件分別在2015年尾及2016年初提交予政府部門。<br />\n<br />\n文件內的圖則顯示，早在2015年11月，港鐵已於西九龍總站B2及B3兩層，詳細規劃一地兩檢設施，包括MCIQ Office（Mainland Customs, Immigration and Quarantine Office），即內地清關、出入境及檢疫設施辦公室，當中包括羈留設施、可容納121至200人的職員休息室、監察及戰術支援組辦公室等，兩層辦公室的面積合共約9.2萬平方呎。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170305/s00001/1488724509981\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170305%2Fs00001%2F1488724509981&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=1ce5573b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170305%2Fs00001%2F1488724509981&h=da3de47f\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170305/s00001/1488724509981</a>"},{"pid":"a1ae1fc8ff88e0d8603475af7b7669ee9967bc88","tid":144883,"uid":12517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T19:45:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}